"どのPayPalボタン（例：Pay Later、Venmo、SEPA、iDEAL、Mercado Pago、Bancontactな"
"ど）が表示されますか？?"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1189
msgid ""
"The PayPal buttons are shown automatically based on several factors, including:"
msgstr "PayPalボタンは、以下を含むいくつかの要因に基づいて自動的に表示されます：:"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1191
