#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1261
msgid "What is PayPal Pay Later?"
msgstr "PayPal Pay Laterとは何ですか？?"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1265
msgid ""
"PayPal Pay Later lets your customers split their purchases into interest-free "
"payments over time, such as \"Pay in 4\" or monthly installments. You get paid in "
"full upfront, while customers enjoy flexible payment options."
msgstr ""
"PayPal Pay Laterは、お客様が「4回払い」や月々の分割払いなど、購入を利息なしで分割"
"できるようにします。あなたは全額を前払いで受け取り、お客様は柔軟な支払いオプション"
"を楽しむことができます。."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1266
msgid ""
"This can help increase your sales, with many merchants seeing higher conversion "
"rates and larger order sizes."
msgstr ""
"これにより、売上を増加させることができ、多くの商人がより高いコンバージョン率と大き"
"な注文サイズを実現しています。."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1269
msgid "Learn more about Pay Later on PayPal’s website."
msgstr "PayPalのウェブサイトで「後払い」について詳しく学ぶ。."

